  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>During your stay at Miilu Northern Lights Cabins, you'll have breakfast included. Each morning you can enjoy a varied breakfast buffet taken at the Miilu Bar &amp; Grill, which is around a 100-metre walk from the cabins.</p>
<p>Upgrade to half-board to include dinner in the Miilu Bar &amp; Grill Restaurant each evening - three-course meals made with seasonal ingredients. The restaurant has lovely views of the frozen lake, so you can admire the Lappish landscape while dining. </p>
<p>A Festive Feast is included for all guests arriving before Christmas, for a Christmas celebration meal with games and music. Please note that the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
