  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Remote location on the shoreline of the beautiful Ylläsjärvi Lake</li>
<li>Around 700 metres walk along a lakeside footpath to the small centre of Ylläsjärvi where you can find the Eelin Kauppa supermarket and a coffee shop</li>
<li>4.5 kilometres to the Ylläsjärvi ski resort</li>
<li>Shuttle service at set times included to Ylläsjärvi Ski Resort</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Ski Bus </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The ski bus is payable locally</li>
<li>Nearest ski bus stop is approx. 700 metres away - the stop is on the main road outside the Eelin Kauppa supermarket</li>
<li>Links to the Ylläsjärvi Ski Resort and the village of Äkäslompolo</li>
<li>Guests aged 6+ with a valid 1-5 day ski pass pay approx. €5 per day to use the ski bus</li>
<li>Guests with a valid 6 day ski pass pay approx. €30 per week</li>
<li>Non-skiers: Day tickets can be purchased on the bus for approx. €13.50 per adult, €8.50 per child (6-11 years)</li>
<li>Children up to 5 years old travel free of charge</li>
<li>Multi-day tickets can be purchased from ticket sales points including the Saaga Hotel reception at the Ylläsjärvi Ski Resort or online</li>
</ul>]]></locationDescription>
