  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Cabins A &amp; B </strong>are around 62m² and sleeps up to six people. Downstairs there is one bedroom with a double bed (160cm) and a separate sleeping alcove with a large single (120cm) bed. Up on the mezzanine level there are three single beds. The apartment has a well-equipped kitchen, lounge area and one bathroom with WC.</p>
<p><strong>Cabin B &amp; C </strong>are around 62m² and sleeps up to six people. Downstairs there is one bedroom with a double bed (160cm). The mezzanine level has three single beds. In the living room there is a sofa bed. The apartment has a well-equipped kitchen, lounge area with a fireplace and one bathroom with WC.</p>
<p>One linen set with towels is included per person, per week. End of stay cleaning is included.</p>
<p><strong>Cabin facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchenette with oven, stove, microwave, toaster, fridge, tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Lounge area</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Terrace with lake views</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Clothes dryer</li>
<li>Washing machine</li>
<li>Bathroom with shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Cots are available upon request (paid locally)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
